Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.88,0:00:14.89,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.12,0:00:15.19,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.87,0:00:18.75,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.41,0:00:23.08,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.08,0:00:26.71,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.71,0:00:30.46,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.46,0:00:33.63,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.01,0:00:36.76,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.76,0:00:40.22,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.31,0:00:44.89,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.89,0:00:48.40,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:51.03,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.11,0:00:54.61,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.78,0:00:59.41,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.41,0:01:02.75,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.25,0:01:11.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato is the Kamen\NRider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.08,0:01:13.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil\NShocker, a secret
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.22,0:01:15.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,organization plotting\Nworld domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.09,0:01:18.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to\Nfight Shocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.20,0:01:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that there?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.98,0:01:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a big one!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.46,0:01:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gonna tip us over!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.32,0:01:57.29,Static Texts,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\fscx100\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HFFFFFF&\b1\pos(493.714,158.5)}The Monstrous Crab Bubbler
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.32,0:01:57.29,Static Texts,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\fscx100\fs145\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HFFFFFF&\b1\pos(522.738,648.451)}Appears in Hokkaido
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.24,0:02:09.24,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H4C6A5E&\3c&H423F1F&}Japan Meteorological Agency Otaru Branch
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.42,0:02:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,"The minor tsunami that\Noccurred yesterday in Osaka Bay
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.23,0:02:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,is the third this month, following\Nsimilar incidents in Kyushu and Shikoku."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.46,0:02:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,"Undersea earthquakes are\Nbelieved to be the cause,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.75,0:02:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,but sabotage to seismometers in the\Nlocal areas prevent their epicenters
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.69,0:02:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,or scales from\Nbeing determined."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.04,0:02:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... what's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.10,0:02:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get so mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.51,0:02:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Japan's always had earthquakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.84,0:02:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If that was all this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.64,0:02:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But why would someone\Nsabotage the seismometers?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.80,0:02:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've heard talk\Nthroughout the agency
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.63,0:02:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,that there's been damage to\Ntheir electrical rooms, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.76,0:02:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Electrical rooms?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.42,0:02:57.35,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H17EEF6&\c&H000000&\an7\fs60}Electrical Room
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.71,0:03:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The seismometer's down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.08,0:03:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Some kind of malfunction?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.25,0:03:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Did we lose power?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.80,0:03:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's been gone a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.44,0:03:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be...\Nthe electrical room...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.47,0:04:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.46,0:04:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.50,0:04:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you,\Nwe don't do four-wheelers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Motorbikes only.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.40,0:04:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.40,0:04:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make me say it again!\NWe don't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.22,0:04:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.82,0:04:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's off around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.61,0:04:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi, where are the girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.40,0:04:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think's got the\NChairman in such a bad mood?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.94,0:04:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,They ran off!\NBabbling about summer break...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they went to Hokkaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.05,0:04:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.53,0:04:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Taki, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.63,0:04:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki's the one who set it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.81,0:04:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki's just as much to blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.71,0:04:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,After all that complaining\Nhe does about the girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.27,0:04:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Chairman,\Nit's not good for you to get so angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.31,0:05:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too old\Nfor this nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.21,0:05:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.99,0:05:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wonder if they know they\Nwon't do much swimming there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.43,0:05:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean how swimming's off\Nlimits because of the tsunami?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.18,0:05:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.62,0:05:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Investigator Taki Kazuya\Nof FBI Tokyo Branch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.76,0:05:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,FBI number 5021.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.96,0:05:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Reporting in as scheduled.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.26,0:05:25.26,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.91,0:05:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing to report\Nas of August 7th.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.96,0:05:29.18,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.97,0:05:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we're through. Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.48,0:05:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki-san?\NHey, this place is so great!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.30,0:05:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's totally groovy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.13,0:05:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Blue skies, fresh air!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.78,0:05:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We're about to go for a swim!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.71,0:05:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to tell you,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.43,0:05:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,but you won't get to show\Noff your swimsuits after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.06,0:06:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?\NWe can't even go swimming?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.83,0:06:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't shoot the messenger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.19,0:06:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The newspapers said swimming\Nis off limits for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.07,0:06:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kanda?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.60,0:06:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Taki?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.42,0:06:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck babysitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.26,0:06:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.55,0:06:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Babysitting? How rude...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.07,0:06:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you gonna come join\Nus, Mr. Taki?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.15,0:06:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,When I'm done with work, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.65,0:06:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,See you, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.29,0:06:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.47,0:06:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I've just received a report\Nfrom Crab Bubbler that he's
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.98,0:06:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,destroyed the seismometer at\Nthe Otaru JMA branch office.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.49,0:06:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Our preparations\Nare now complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.56,0:06:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Based on our successful trials in\NKyushu, Shikoku, and Osaka,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.71,0:06:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll use our new underwater bombs,\Nmore powerful than a nuclear explosion,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.65,0:06:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,to create a tsunami on\Nthe Muroran Peninsula.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.82,0:06:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Until our plan is\Nsuccessful, we must not let
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.72,0:06:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,anyone learn the secret\Nof this operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.43,0:06:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Have Crab Bubbler continue his\Nsurveillance on the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.76,0:07:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, no diving allowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.78,0:07:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The water's off limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.74,0:07:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay out of my business.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.15,0:07:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be your life\Non the line...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.76,0:07:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Crab Bubbler,\Norders from our leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.16,0:07:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're to kill anyone who\Ngets close to our base.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.01,0:07:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.49,0:07:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.09,0:07:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's such a shame. The water's so\Ncalm, but we still can't swim?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.99,0:07:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I spent 3500 yen\Non this swimsuit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.98,0:07:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Like anyone cares.\NAm I right, Mr. Kanda?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.33,0:07:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.52,0:08:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.52,0:08:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, let's go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.54,0:08:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.51,0:08:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.13,0:08:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We just got here.\NNow we have to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.35,0:08:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No fun at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.05,0:08:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...\Nthey took my Shocker transceiver!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.49,0:08:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.72,0:08:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're sure the diver was dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.00,0:08:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.25,0:08:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's this mini-transceiver\Nyou said you found?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.53,0:08:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It has an odd-looking\Neagle symbol on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.65,0:09:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kanda, please stay\Nwhere you are for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.96,0:09:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to tell Ichimonji\NHayato about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.98,0:09:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato? Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.62,0:09:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's like a modern\Nsuperhero, I guess you'd say.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.23,0:09:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.64,0:09:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Any who learn about our\Nunderwater earthquakes must die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.91,0:09:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But I won't kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.22,0:09:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll convert that able body of yours\Nand put you to work as a cyborg!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.11,0:09:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Underwater earthquakes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.19,0:09:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.46,0:09:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you're the one\Nbehind the tsunamis?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.00,0:09:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be absurd...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.00,0:09:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to stop you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.37,0:09:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kanda!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.52,0:09:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening, Mr. Kanda?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.73,0:10:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a feeling Shocker was\Nbehind those mysterious tsunamis,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.94,0:10:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and what do you\Nknow, here they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.57,0:10:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.84,0:10:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.05,0:10:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.57,0:10:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep driving! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.55,0:11:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.13,0:11:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.83,0:11:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker HQ! Shocker...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.15,0:11:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider.\NThey're the ones behind the tsunamis!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.04,0:11:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing work, Mr. Kanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.63,0:12:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can trace this\Ntransceiver's frequency...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.16,0:12:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Get down! It's about to explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.01,0:12:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider, we won't be able\Nto find their base now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.65,0:12:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.05,0:12:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll find their\Nbase, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.33,0:12:21.26,Bumper Episode 14-51,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs85\pos(311,454)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.66,0:12:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Crab Bubbler.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.90,0:12:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider stole your\Nmini-transceiver, did he?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.57,0:12:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.73,0:12:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But I detonated it immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.39,0:12:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool! Do not\Nunderestimate Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.02,0:12:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What if he were to listen\Nin on our communications?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.27,0:12:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What would happen\Nthen, Crab Bubbler?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.21,0:12:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He could easily find this base's location\Nthrough the use of a directional tracker.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.94,0:12:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, my leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.66,0:12:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.95,0:12:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider is on our scent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We have not one moment to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.27,0:13:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You must destroy the seismometer of the\NSapporo Central Weather Station at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.37,0:13:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,As you just heard,\Nmy scientists,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.25,0:13:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,now that the Rider is on our\Ntrail, we must hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.22,0:13:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare for the\Ndetonation at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.83,0:13:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We need but two\Nhours, my leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.73,0:13:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.07,0:13:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Spark a massive tsunami in the\Nsea near Otaru in two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.45,0:13:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kanda!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.59,0:13:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.73,0:13:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mari, where's Kanda?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.55,0:13:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.53,0:13:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kanda,\Nwhere's the transceiver?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.64,0:13:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I have Hayato looking into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.70,0:13:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.24,0:13:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So he really is here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.09,0:13:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.77,0:13:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I can locate the special\Ncommunications signal they're using,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.15,0:14:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can inevitably determine\Nthe Shocker frequency.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.54,0:14:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.16,0:14:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Extremely short\Nwaves, 384 megahertz!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.89,0:14:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.05,0:14:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kanda explained everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.70,0:14:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.84,0:14:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So, did you determine\NShocker's frequency?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.45,0:14:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find it, Hayato?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.81,0:14:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Extremely short\Nwaves, 384 megahertz.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.02,0:14:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.25,0:14:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If we use our directional tracker, we\Ncan find the location of Shocker's base.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.48,0:14:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.10,0:14:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have you do that, Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.38,0:14:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker will be feeling the heat and\Nracing to destroy that seismometer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.15,0:14:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll investigate the Sapporo\NCentral Weather Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.57,0:14:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll contact HAM radio enthusiasts\Nin the area and try to trace back
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.95,0:14:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the source of the waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.70,0:14:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to it, Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.51,0:14:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you help us, Mr. Kanda?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.91,0:14:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.81,0:14:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.12,0:15:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen. We're going to contact\NHAM radio operators in this area
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.00,0:15:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and ask about the directionality\Nof the mystery waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.03,0:15:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we chart the directions\Non the map, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.18,0:15:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,CQCQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.64,0:15:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This is JA8AGN.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.94,0:15:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Emergency transmission.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.56,0:15:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Please report the direction in\Nwhich you hear the extremely
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.03,0:15:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,short wave 384 megahertz signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.67,0:15:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I repeat...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.10,0:15:37.03,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H000000&\c&H999C9A&}Sapporo District Meteorological Observatory
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.12,0:15:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... was I too late?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.16,0:15:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's them! They did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.62,0:15:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.65,0:16:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.99,0:16:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This is JA8BIX Hakodate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.55,0:16:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Direction is north-northwest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.09,0:16:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.\NHakodate, north-northwest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.67,0:16:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hakodate, north-northwest...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.92,0:17:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, talk! Where is your base?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.16,0:17:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,West-northwest from Kushiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.87,0:17:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,North-northwest from Otaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.37,0:17:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We seem to have our\Ngeneral direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.36,0:17:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Fifty kilometers north-northwest\Ninto the sea off Otaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.27,0:18:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.65,0:18:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,How is the explosion coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.94,0:18:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Preparations are complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.53,0:18:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The large tsunami will occur in\Nthe sea off Otaru in ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.53,0:19:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done. Evacuate, all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.33,0:19:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato, any luck?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.31,0:19:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you trace back the signal?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.09,0:19:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.44,0:19:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a life-saver, Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.66,0:19:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell the other three, as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.48,0:19:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,that Hayato says thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.83,0:19:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck, Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.26,0:20:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.83,0:20:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.94,0:20:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! The bombs will\Ngo off in seven minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.00,0:20:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We must evacuate at once! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.27,0:20:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.33,0:20:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like I arrived with\Nseven minutes to spare!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.40,0:21:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Can't see now, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.45,0:22:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider... die!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.26,0:22:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.74,0:22:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Feels great out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.86,0:22:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.35,0:22:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a romantic sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.23,0:22:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess even our girls can feel\Nromantic from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.46,0:22:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.20,0:22:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.36,0:22:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.65,0:22:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, you guys?\NAren't you going to swim?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.94,0:23:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought swimming\Nwas off limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.13,0:23:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's safe now. Right, Hayato?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.18,0:23:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.51,0:23:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay then, let's have a swim!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.13,0:23:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna grab my bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.61,0:23:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.44,0:23:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato, shall we join them?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.66,0:23:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Let's race!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.80,0:23:26.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With his wonderful allies by his side,\NIchimonji Hayato, the Kamen Rider,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.63,0:23:29.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,foiled Shocker's\Nartificial tsunami plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.26,0:23:30.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.67,0:23:33.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shocker, do your worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.94,0:23:35.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I'm not in this alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.72,0:23:37.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I have wonderful\Nallies by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.88,0:23:39.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Allies!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.91,0:23:40.50,Cont,,0,0,0,,{\blur.8\fad(0,470)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.91,0:23:43.33,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(499.031,496.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.15,0:23:45.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.48,0:23:47.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is the fire-breathing caterpillar\Nmonster, Dokugander.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.85,0:23:49.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The man-eating caterpillar\Nthat appears out of the blue
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.59,0:23:51.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,turns out to be the Shocker\Nmonster, Dokugander.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.63,0:23:53.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,When Kamen Rider\Npursues the beast,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.44,0:23:56.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,it leads to a tempestuous\Nconfrontation with Dokugander.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.36,0:24:00.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week for "The Fire-Breathing\NCaterpillar Monster, Dokugander."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.01,0:24:00.89,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs105\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(497.167,210.389)}The Fire-Breathing Caterpillar Monster
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.01,0:24:00.89,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(527.167,660.389)}Dokugander
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.84,0:24:10.68,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.26,0:24:13.26,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.26,0:24:15.22,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.22,0:24:18.27,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the\Nvillains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.77,0:24:20.64,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.64,0:24:22.52,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.52,0:24:24.31,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.31,0:24:25.65,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.11,0:24:28.15,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.20,0:24:33.87,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with\Nall of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.87,0:24:37.45,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.45,0:24:41.04,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.54,0:24:45.29,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:51.32,0:01:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The Monstrous Crab Bubbler Appears in Hokkaido